channel.title: Why Not? - Dev. Team
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://img142.imageshack.us/img142/2331/whynotws8.jpg[/img]
[i]Yes, another damn project team! But I will stick with it this time...[/i]
[b]Most of you know me and my teams. Inconsistent. Not on task. Never working. Inactive. And all this includes me - although I did work... I am known for making teams that never get ANYWHERE. >.<. It happens. But let's see if I can end this spree of happenings? Say, maybe make a team for a project with strict guidelines? Because I know most of you look at my topics, say "Forget this, another inconsistent team" and leave. Trust me - this WILL NOT happen this time. Are you ready for this? Newb is changing his ways of being a "loner."
~ Newb 2341[/b]
[b]Join the forums for coding... [url=http://whynot.smfforfree3.com/index.php]Here they be.[/url][/b]
[u]Team Guidelines[/u] 1. Be active on these forums, doing coding, and on the coding forums. Easy said. I will boot you if you are not. 2. Must be able to work independently. Yes, I will allow small teams, or "partners," to work on a big task from time to time, but don't expect lots... 3. Must be over 20 rep - if not, how about this - be very ENTHUSIASTIC about coding, active, and have some prowess at the skill. 4. Must own a good server - AKA Horror-Moss, ZdiddyScape, PK Isle. 5. Finally, have to like me and my works.
[u]Team List[/u] [i]Leaders:[/i] [b]Do everything - teach, help, show, code.[/b] 1. Newb 2341 2. I Br3ndan I 3. killah246 4. Nirvana [i]Server Coders:[/i] [b]Code the server, every file, everything.[/b] 1. I Metal I 2. KiIIler (may work with I Br3ndan I to learn more of my ways.) [i]Client Coder(s):[/i] [b]Make a client for the server.[/b] 1. Killah246 (most likely will accept) 2. [i]Advertisers:[/i] [b]Advertise the site on here and other forums.[/b] 1. mod robby 2. 3.
[u]Server Plans[/u] [i]Many. I have high expectations for this server. We have a great team, so we SHOULD have a great server...[/i] [b]1. Unique but fun. Very fun. So fun that CMs and MODs like it. 2. All skills hopefully, I Br3ndan I seems good at these. 3. New stuff, starting equip., place, etc. 4. A brand new type of PKing. 5. Quests if possible. People should have something to do... 6. Much more that me and the team shall disscuss.[/b]
[u]Team Spot App.[/u] [b]Use this app. format to be accepted or declined by me... PS, this is supposed to have bad grammer.[/b] ;) [i]*** is needed field...[/i] [code] [b]*** What spot are you be wanting?: [/b] [b]Do you enjoy my work?: [/b] [b]*** Why should I accept you.: [/b] [b]*** Examples of your work, URLs?: [/b] [b]If needed, would you die for the team?: [/b] [b]Have you ever worked with me?: [/b] [b]*** How long can you be on here?: [/b] [b]Last one - ORLY, is it important?: [/b][/code]
[b]My last words - this WILL NOT FAIL.[/b][/center]
